Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.67,0:00:05.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.35,0:00:13.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.59,0:00:33.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.31,0:00:36.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The sound resonates\NInto my heart, so hard and deep
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.29,0:00:40.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A field of stars spans endlessly\NAnd through it I carve a passageway
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.25,0:00:42.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In step with time as generations change
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.19,0:00:44.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Close your eyes and listen closely
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.22,0:00:47.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shooting stars stream on silently…\Nuntil the goodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.29,0:00:50.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Keep the light inside of you,\Nnever give up don't ever lose
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.29,0:00:52.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Transcend time and you will prove,\Nthere is a special place for you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.14,0:00:53.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A blaze of glory is there,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.93,0:00:55.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's all a part of our estate;\Nlife is our story to create
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.75,0:01:01.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.64,0:01:05.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wishes speak from ages old by voice of light\NThroughout the age, never fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.56,0:01:09.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A secret fire, a scream of light,\Nvoices calling through twilight
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.29,0:01:11.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Cast your thoughts to the wind,\Nhang your wishes on the moon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.39,0:01:13.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Live your life with all your strength\Nfor dreams will reach you very soon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.25,0:01:16.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.96,0:01:19.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wishes speak from ages old\Nby voice of light
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.14,0:01:21.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Throughout the age,\Nnever fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.29,0:01:24.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Someday your dream will find\Nits place somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.68,0:01:28.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Keep shining like a star
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.88,0:01:36.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A cursed parakeet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.55,0:01:41.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, all his past owners had\Nterrible things happen and died.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.29,0:01:44.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious? That's bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.34,0:01:47.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want him, Shigeo?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.38,0:01:51.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Not after you tell me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.96,0:01:54.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you go dump\Nhim someplace?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.36,0:01:56.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But…that's cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.29,0:01:58.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How about you, Chad?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.29,0:01:59.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's cute, y'know?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.33,0:02:02.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.85,0:02:04.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chad has a weakness\Nfor cute things like…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.29,0:02:10.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wha--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.29,0:02:24.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We shall continue to devour…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.88,0:02:28.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In order to fill the emptiness\Nof our existence,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.96,0:02:31.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,we must continue to devour.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.63,0:02:37.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A Soul Reaper's soul is\Nexceptionally delicious…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.96,0:02:42.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Once you taste it,\Nyou always crave it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.13,0:02:56.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,C-Chad!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.63,0:03:00.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you all right, Chad?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.75,0:03:03.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.00,0:03:06.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Fine?! You're bleeding!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.67,0:03:09.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for saving me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.60,0:03:10.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.67,0:03:14.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Yuichi Shibata.\NWhat's yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.80,0:03:17.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.21,0:03:19.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's like it understood\Nwhat just happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.88,0:03:21.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This parakeet is cursed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.97,0:03:23.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's your name, Mister?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.96,0:03:27.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yasutora Sado.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.17,0:03:30.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm 15 years old…still.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.85,0:03:33.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Chad is interested in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.09,0:03:41.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Geez… I can't believe my injuries\Nhealed in a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.23,0:03:43.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.88,0:03:47.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I was among the best in\Nmy Kido class.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.29,0:03:48.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That was easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.30,0:03:51.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kido class? So what…?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.00,0:03:53.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Soul Reapers go to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.00,0:03:55.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Well yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.17,0:03:57.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But Ichigo…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.00,0:03:59.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How do you drink this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.92,0:04:04.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You just poke\Na straw in it and drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.13,0:04:05.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Straw?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.59,0:04:09.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're together again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.29,0:04:10.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.84,0:04:12.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are quite close, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.10,0:04:15.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mizuiro… Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.29,0:04:18.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do we look like friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.42,0:04:20.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.00,0:04:23.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well, if you say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.29,0:04:28.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But Ichigo, you should be more\Naware of what people will think.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.13,0:04:32.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid, if I cared about\Nwhat people thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.29,0:04:34.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'd have dyed my hair black.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.00,0:04:36.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.29,0:04:37.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So this is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.13,0:04:41.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But where do I poke this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.38,0:04:45.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hello Kuchiki!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.21,0:04:49.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Helloo! Err…Kojima.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.34,0:04:53.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Right! I haven't introduced\Nmyself yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.29,0:04:56.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Mizuiro Kojima, age 15. I like…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.31,0:04:57.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Picking up girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.31,0:04:58.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.97,0:04:59.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.00,0:05:02.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He looks like a dork,\Nbut he's a real flirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.85,0:05:03.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.13,0:05:07.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! You'll ruin my reputation!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.29,0:05:11.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I'm only interested\Nin older women.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.29,0:05:13.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's why she has to be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.30,0:05:14.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.59,0:05:18.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.29,0:05:20.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.01,0:05:22.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There's the beautiful new transfer,\NKuchiki!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.97,0:05:24.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.71,0:05:26.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo lured her here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.09,0:05:27.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.85,0:05:30.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Ichigo, why you…!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.67,0:05:31.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.42,0:05:35.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,T-Thanks. You're so happy\Nyou're crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.25,0:05:39.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad you've come, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.29,0:05:41.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,To this garden of masculinity!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.88,0:05:42.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.96,0:05:46.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Awright, everyone!\NWe're partying it up during lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.51,0:05:48.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,With milk coffee and\Nyakisoba bread?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.60,0:05:50.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! It's the spirit that counts!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.29,0:05:52.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And Kuchiki…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.31,0:05:55.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you're ever in need,\Ndon't hesitate to come to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.20,0:05:57.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.29,0:05:59.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.21,0:06:01.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Chad…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.88,0:06:02.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.59,0:06:05.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you injured?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.29,0:06:09.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey yeah, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.42,0:06:12.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A steel beam fell on my head yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.47,0:06:14.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A steel beam?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.19,0:06:18.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,As for my hand, I had\N a collision with a motorcycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.63,0:06:25.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And the rider got hurt bad…\Nso I just carried him to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.50,0:06:27.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,N-No wonder you were late.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.96,0:06:31.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But geez, what is\Nyour body made of?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.00,0:06:34.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's with the bird?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.09,0:06:39.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, my name is Yuichi Shibata.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.88,0:06:41.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.34,0:06:46.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this is amazing!\NIt really talks!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.21,0:06:49.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Keigo Asano.\NCan you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.29,0:06:52.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chad, where'd you get the bird?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.42,0:06:54.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.21,0:07:01.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Someone gave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.24,0:07:02.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.09,0:07:06.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You were just about to tell us,\Nbut got lazy and cut it short, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.59,0:07:09.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's a bad habit you have.\NNow, explain!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.22,0:07:10.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't cut it short.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.22,0:07:13.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yes you did! Listen you…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.29,0:07:15.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.22,0:07:15.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.29,0:07:19.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There's definitely something\Nin that bird, but it's not evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.50,0:07:22.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably a lonely spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.29,0:07:25.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But we cannot leave it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.67,0:07:31.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We should perform a Konso tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.13,0:07:35.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Got it. Another sleepless night.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.46,0:07:37.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't complain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.30,0:07:39.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah-yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.00,0:07:41.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Still…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.17,0:07:45.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He sensed a spirit and worried\Nabout the safety of the others…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.75,0:07:47.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps he's beginning to\Nunderstand
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.29,0:07:49.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,what it means\Nto be a Soul Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.92,0:07:50.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.87,0:07:52.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.29,0:07:55.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It was during 8th grade…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.31,0:07:56.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.13,0:07:58.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,...when I first met Chad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.59,0:08:05.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Back then, my hair color got\Npeople's attention
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.29,0:08:07.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and got me into fights.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.80,0:08:11.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It was when I got into\Nthis little scrape.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.09,0:08:27.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.56,0:08:39.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.25,0:08:59.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chad never fights back,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.10,0:09:00.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,no matter how much\Npeople goad him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.46,0:09:03.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's an odd one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.84,0:09:04.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.29,0:09:08.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This juice is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.96,0:09:09.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.09,0:09:16.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.96,0:09:19.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki Clinic\NInternal Medicine - Pediatrics\N		Outta the way! Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.75,0:09:22.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's the matter, Karin?\NWhat's your hurry?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.46,0:09:24.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hi Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.29,0:09:27.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.29,0:09:29.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,An accident!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.01,0:09:31.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There was a car accident\Nat the intersection.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.55,0:09:32.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Car accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.92,0:09:34.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You won't take him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.88,0:09:35.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.85,0:09:39.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There are patients who need more\Nthan our first-aid level of treatment!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.29,0:09:43.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now listen! Tell your director\Nit's a request from Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.67,0:09:47.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then you'll find some free beds!\NUnderstand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.21,0:09:50.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dad…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.84,0:09:53.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn useless people!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.00,0:09:55.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Anything I can do to help?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.56,0:09:56.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.75,0:10:00.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Get back in some corner and\Nstay outta the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.17,0:10:06.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, one more patient!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.93,0:10:07.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.29,0:10:11.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Man, he's a big one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.84,0:10:13.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo, come here and get to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.71,0:10:14.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.30,0:10:16.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.84,0:10:18.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.48,0:10:37.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's a terrible wound…!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.29,0:10:38.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.45,0:10:42.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like a burn.\NWhat hit you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.92,0:10:44.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This feeling…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.92,0:10:47.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have to take it\Neasy for awhile.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.10,0:10:47.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.05,0:10:48.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.84,0:10:51.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm…okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.29,0:10:53.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.64,0:10:56.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way you're fine\Nafter losing so much blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.84,0:10:59.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You see?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.38,0:11:02.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzu! Karin!\NGet a bed ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.17,0:11:06.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Let's get you to bed, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.42,0:11:10.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Did you feel it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.00,0:11:11.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.29,0:11:13.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I felt it even in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.09,0:11:17.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't sense anything\Nfrom the parakeet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.29,0:11:19.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But his injury...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.29,0:11:21.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,smelled of Hollow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.92,0:12:04.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki Clinic\NInternal Medicine - Pediatrics
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.96,0:12:08.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,'Morning!\NBrother, breakfast is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.63,0:12:10.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Karin?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.96,0:12:12.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't want breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.13,0:12:15.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think she feels well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.31,0:12:18.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Her? Not feeling well?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.63,0:12:20.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.26,0:12:21.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.21,0:12:22.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Bad news!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.22,0:12:24.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chad has disappeared from his room!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.71,0:12:29.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.29,0:12:32.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.84,0:12:34.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Any clues about\Nwhere he went?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.17,0:12:36.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No, how about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.96,0:12:37.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No luck either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.29,0:12:41.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There's no news at the Soul Society\Nabout a Hollow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.24,0:12:42.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can't find anything\Non the radar either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.50,0:12:47.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Usually, Hollows hide themselves\Nbetween this world and the Soul Society,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.31,0:12:51.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,except when they\Ncommit foul deeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.29,0:12:54.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Even if Hollows are after Chad,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.29,0:12:55.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,we won't be able to\Nget the location
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.89,0:12:59.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,unless they show\Nthemselves in this world. Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.09,0:13:02.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You expect me to understand\Nwith those kindergarten drawings?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.55,0:13:06.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A Hollow is targeting Chad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.00,0:13:09.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be too late if we wait\Nuntil he's attacked!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.29,0:13:11.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There has to be something…!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.38,0:13:15.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! The parakeet Chad had!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.21,0:13:18.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We just have to follow\Nthe soul that possessed it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.50,0:13:20.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's not possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.41,0:13:21.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.29,0:13:39.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichi...go? What's this sensation?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.96,0:13:51.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mister…you're nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.84,0:13:52.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.51,0:13:56.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I need to apologize to you, Mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.71,0:14:01.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, everyone who\Nowns me gets bad luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.84,0:14:03.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.46,0:14:08.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I didn't tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.29,0:14:09.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.21,0:14:11.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.29,0:14:16.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So Mister, forget about me…\Nand abandon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.55,0:14:19.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mister…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.25,0:14:21.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.09,0:14:32.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichi…go…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.29,0:14:38.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I must tell him…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.30,0:14:41.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How can this be…?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.84,0:14:46.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's such a weak soul,\Neven I cannot sense its presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.17,0:14:49.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And he's trying to find it from\Nthis distance?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.28,0:14:58.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is…?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.48,0:14:59.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I found him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.84,0:15:01.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.59,0:15:06.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Those were..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.75,0:15:09.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Spirit Ribbons, visible rays\Nof spiritual energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.96,0:15:11.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Only high-level Soul Reapers\Nare able to see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.38,0:15:16.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Has he progressed that much\Nin this short time?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.71,0:15:20.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we lost him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.46,0:15:23.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mister, you don't have\Nto do this anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.29,0:15:25.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right, I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.38,0:15:28.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Being tough is my one good trait.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.46,0:15:34.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.92,0:15:39.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He found us! Let's get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.00,0:15:41.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mister…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.42,0:15:43.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. This is nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.55,0:15:52.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.29,0:15:53.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's Chad!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.46,0:16:00.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot!\NWhy's he running?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.29,0:16:01.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.59,0:16:02.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.55,0:16:05.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Karin!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.80,0:16:07.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing?\NYou're still so weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.25,0:16:10.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Karin!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.96,0:16:12.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.38,0:16:15.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Take her home first.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.71,0:16:18.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go and save him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.84,0:16:22.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What're you saying?! I can't…!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.29,0:16:23.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't complain!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.75,0:16:27.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you leave her there and go,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.09,0:16:30.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,you'll be distracted when\Nyou fight the Hollow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.22,0:16:31.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can't have that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.81,0:16:36.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Understand? Now go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.96,0:16:38.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.46,0:16:44.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You…haven't gotten enough of\Nyour powers back to fight a Hollow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.29,0:16:48.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take chances.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.46,0:16:50.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.29,0:16:55.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I'd make\Nyou worry by messing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.92,0:16:58.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.59,0:17:00.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.30,0:17:07.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, Karin?\NHang on! This isn't like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.71,0:17:09.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.21,0:17:12.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I...saw it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.75,0:17:15.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Last night...the memories of the spirit\Nthat possessed the parakeet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.29,0:17:19.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's because I was\Nthe closest in age.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.25,0:17:23.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The strongest memory that\Nremains in that child's mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.97,0:17:26.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It came flowing into me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.55,0:17:32.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That child... His mother was killed\Nright before his very eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.29,0:17:36.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Please...Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.13,0:17:40.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Please...save...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.03,0:17:43.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,that child!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.05,0:17:45.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.37,0:17:51.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! I can't overtake them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.50,0:17:55.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If I were not in this gigai,\Nit would be easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.71,0:17:58.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it that the physical powers\Nof a gigai are the same
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.29,0:18:00.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,as for an average human being?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.59,0:18:02.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Those dolts at the technology\Ndevelopment bureau!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.24,0:18:05.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No...I'm starting to run\Nout of breath!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.56,0:18:09.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What a nice smell!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.59,0:18:31.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You smell delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.38,0:18:34.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let me devour...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.29,0:18:36.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,that soul of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.26,0:18:42.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... You won't die in just one shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.55,0:18:47.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And it seems you can see me, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.42,0:18:49.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Just...who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.96,0:18:55.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The one who reigns!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.59,0:18:58.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mask of flesh, all creation,\N flap of wings...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.72,0:19:00.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,the one who carries\Nthe title of human!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.19,0:19:02.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In the name of truth and temperance,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.31,0:19:05.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,dig your claws into\Nthe wall of sinless dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.00,0:19:07.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Destruction Spell 33...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.19,0:19:08.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Pale Fire Crash!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.05,0:19:12.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It worked!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.29,0:19:15.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Good, at least this much\Nof my powers are back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.30,0:19:22.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What was that noise?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.63,0:19:24.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She's being attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.59,0:19:28.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The lady who was after us\Nearlier is being attacked
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.60,0:19:31.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,by the one who is after us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.29,0:19:34.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.25,0:19:36.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.34,0:19:37.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.96,0:19:38.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to save her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.46,0:19:41.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No, you can't! It's too dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.13,0:19:50.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't mean I'm in danger\Nof being hit by a car
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.39,0:19:54.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,if you leave me in the road!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.29,0:19:55.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No, Mister...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.25,0:19:57.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You can't see ghosts!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.93,0:20:01.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No! He'll get you! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.26,0:20:03.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mister! Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.46,0:20:07.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ridiculous! It didn't even scratch him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.29,0:20:11.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hah! I know that trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.06,0:20:13.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Soul Reaper spell, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.29,0:20:18.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But yours is so weak.\NI felt nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.83,0:20:20.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.80,0:20:25.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought, my Kido hasn't recovered\Nenough to use a spell of that level.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.29,0:20:28.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I get it, you're a Soul Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.92,0:20:32.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder you smell so yummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.71,0:20:35.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A Soul Reaper, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.26,0:20:36.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.29,0:20:44.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I've devoured two Soul Reapers\Nwho tried to help that kid pass over.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.96,0:20:49.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They were delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.88,0:20:54.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,By kid, do you mean the spirit\Ninside that parakeet?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.59,0:20:55.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.13,0:20:59.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you keep chasing\Nafter that soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.92,0:21:00.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.72,0:21:07.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you'll let me eat you\Nwithout resisting, I'll tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.26,0:21:08.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why you--!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.42,0:21:18.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.25,0:21:22.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tell him...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.17,0:21:25.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That if he passes over,\Nhe'll be able to see his mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.50,0:21:27.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tell that boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.42,0:21:33.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let that boy be\Nall alone anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.29,0:21:34.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Please Ichigo...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.93,0:22:04.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Though the voyage must continue on
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.29,0:22:08.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,May seas always be calm
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.29,0:22:14.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When the cycle of the moon\Nhas renewed may it shine
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.29,0:22:19.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's light to guide your boat
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.59,0:22:23.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I offer this voyage a prayer
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.09,0:22:28.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,With each new day that still awaits
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.26,0:22:33.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,On vividly shining seas
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.29,0:22:40.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,To the end of the journey
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.59,0:22:44.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Urahara Shop,\Nwhere Soul Reapers often visit...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.22,0:22:46.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Urahara Kisuke, the shop owner\Nwho carries a dangerous scent on him...
